""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" => Visual mode related
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" Visual mode pressing * or # searches for the current selection
" Super useful! From an idea by Michael Naumann vnoremap <silent> * :call VisualSelection('f', '')<CR>
