map j gj
map k gk

" search
nmap <leader>s :%s/
vmap <leader>s :s/

" scroll the viewport faster
nnoremap <C-e> 10<C-e>
nnoremap <C-y> 10<C-y>

" Map <Space> to / (search) and Ctrl-<Space> to ? (backwards search)
